": \"her unique perspective\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"our coverage\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"saidRebecca Chatman\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"Vice President\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"Coordinating Producer\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"NBC Olympics Production\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weggemann has enjoyed a decorated 15+ year athletic career.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weggemann\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"a decorated 15+ year athletic career\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her Paralympic debut at the 2012 London Games, she won gold in the 50m freestyle S8 and bronze in the 4x100m medley relay.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.353629700365358e-13, \"text\": \"4x100m medley relay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her Paralympic debut\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 London Games\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50m freestyle S8\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has since competed at both the Rio and Tokyo Paralympics, winning three more medals (two gold) at the latter.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1322, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999336069, \"rank\": 6.644946