wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trifluoroacetic_acid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trifluoroacetic_acid\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peacock\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"Weggemann\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"her husband\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"their company\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The film chronicles Weggemann's training period for the Tokyo Paralympics through the COVID-19 pandemic, as well as their journey to parenthood, shining a light on their struggles with infertility and IVF when starting a family.Watershedwill be available to stream on Peacock this summer.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999846154425, \"rank\": 1.5381865768434595e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999999996425686, \"rank\": 2.72514984806301e-10, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}, {\"begin\": 1957, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999942897375, \"rank\": 5.709314903671352e-09, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The film\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"Weggemann's training period\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"their journey\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"parenthood\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"a light\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"their struggles\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"infertility\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"IVF\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"Watershedwill\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am beyond grateful for the entire team at NBC Sports for supporting me as I realize two dreams - hosting during an Olympic Games, while simultaneously preparing to compete in the Paralympics.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2024, \"end\": 2034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999996656816269, \"rank\": 3.3412911097035765e-07, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the entire team\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a new mom, it is important to show my daughter that motherhood is a comma, not a period.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new mom\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"that motherhood\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"a comma\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"a period\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a disabled woman, I am also aware that this moment offers a path forward for others,\\\" said Weggemann.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disabled woman\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"a path\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"Weggemann\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Far too often, stories of disability are told for us, not by us.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stories\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"disability\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why when Jay and I began development onWatershed,one of our driving forces was to change that narrative.\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jay\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"our driving forces\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"that narrative\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are honored that our filmhas found a home in Peacock and hope it continues to serve as a beacon for others who find themselves navigating their own watershed moments.\\\"\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999942897375, \"rank\": 5.709314903671352e-09, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our filmhas\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"a home\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2593}, {\"ngram\": \"a beacon\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2647}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"their own watershed moments\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weggemann is also an inclusion advocate on the Advisory Board of Disability for Delta Air Lines and in March 2021 published her first book,Limitless: The Power of Hope and Resilience to Overcome Circumstance, detailing her personal a